<DOC><DOCNO> DOE2-60-0258 </DOCNO><TEXT>This volume contain papers presented at a conference on the impacts ofmodern technology on mine productivity and economy. Papers are groupedunder four themes which include: capital requirements, organization andproductivity in mechanized mining; developments in shaft sinking; mechanizedscaling and rock support; mining in arctic conditions. Relevant papersare abstracted separately.</TEXT></DOC>